Trace in accounting records all purchased breeding stocks and record the same in the BSLC; and 

Update the columns in the BSLC pertaining to births of offspring and stock dispositions, and draw the necessary accounting journal entries to adjust the balance of Breeding Stocks in the books of accounts;

